{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"60361f39cb","title":"《中央对武汉军区公告的复电》","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f8af80fef4","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":25,"articleId":"60361f39cb","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ddcdaf3cc2","type":"title","text":"《中央对武汉军区公告的复电》","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"60361f39cb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a97450aa59","type":"paragraph","text":"林、周、中央文革小组：","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"60361f39cb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0b4daa139a","type":"paragraph","text":"拟复电如下，请讨论酌定。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"60361f39cb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7397a7c349","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"60361f39cb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6c305faa28","type":"paragraph","text":"一、你们现在所采取的立场和政策是正确的，公告可以发表。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"60361f39cb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"42aa070c54","type":"paragraph","text":"二、对于犯了严重错误的干部，包括你们和广大革命群众所要打倒的陈再道同志在内，只要他们不再坚持错误，认真改正，并得到群众谅解了以后，仍然可以站起来参加革命行列。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"60361f39cb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6c213664fd","type":"paragraph","text":"三、要向思想不通的某些人员和百万雄师群众做工作，使他们转变过来。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"60361f39cb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb922d2ac7","type":"paragraph","text":"四、要向左派做工作，不要乘机报复。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"60361f39cb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"94e86ea6bf","type":"paragraph","text":"五、要警惕坏人捣乱，不许破坏社会秩序。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"60361f39cb","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":617,"end":617}}}},"__N_SSG":true}